WEBVTT

00:00.600 --> 00:02.980
She has lightened up a great deal.

00:03.580 --> 00:07.660
Much of it seems to do with a new friend she’s developed in the last few months.

00:08.140 --> 00:13.500
Additionally, she has had a change in her living arrangement, which she seems to be happy with.

00:15.260 --> 00:22.740
Having now found a friend her own age, she will probably develop a relationship with that person that is more intimate than the one she has with me.

00:23.920 --> 00:29.880
I wonder if she still asks me questions because she doesn’t know what else to talk about.

00:31.020 --> 00:34.520
I will see how things go for the next few months, and then I would like to discontinue examinations.
